  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "12 Indian fishermen arrested at Peduruthuduwa beach",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that 12 Indian fishermen were arrested yesterday (03rd) along with an Indian trawler who had illegally entered the coast near Pedurutuduwa, Jaffna.",
        "A group of officers belonging to the Northern Naval Command arrested the Indian fishermen while they were fishing in Peduruthuduwa beach.",
        "The Navy took steps to take the Indian fishermen along with the fishing vessel along with the fish they caught along with the fishing gear and bring them to the land according to the existing sanitary measures.",
        "The Navy took steps to hand over the arrested 12 Indian fishermen to the Jaffna Fisheries Inspectorate for further investigation."
      ],
